         The Project was won by Solenergi Power Private Ltd. (SPPL) within the 750MWac Rewa Ultra Mega Solar Park in the Rewa district of Madhya Pradesh, India.  


           


         The Project will be developed by Arinsun Clean Energy Private Limited (the Company), a subsidiary of SPPL. The solar park is being developed by Rewa Ultra Mega Solar Limited (RUMSL), a joint venture between Madhya Pradesh Urja Vikas Nigam Limited (MPUVNL)  a Madhya Pradesh State Government agency and the Solar Energy Corporation of India (SECI).  


           


         The Project is expected to be commissioned by December 2018. The off-takers for the Project will be Madhya Pradesh Power Management Company Limited (MPPMCL) and Delhi Metro Rail Corporation (DMRC).

