         The solar park is located across five villages, namely, Badwar, Barsaita Desh, Barsaita Pahad, Etar Pahad and Ramnagar Pahad under Gurh Tehsil in Rewa District, MP. The solar park is equally divided into three units, each of which will have a 250 MWac solar power plant. SPPL has won project development rights for Unit III of the park.
